column2: # Fit the full model with interaction and all controls

lm(formula = `Weight Change (lbs)` ~ sleep_risk * stress_risk + 
    physical_activity + age_group + Gender + `Daily Caloric Surplus/Deficit` + 
    `BMR (Calories)` + `Duration (weeks)`, data = Health)
`Mean Weight Change` = mean(`Weight Change (lbs)`, na.rm = TRUE),
lm_weight <- lm(`Weight Change (lbs)` ~ stress_risk * age_group, data = Health)

lm(formula = `Weight Change (lbs)` ~ stress_risk * age_group, 
    data = Health)
`Mean Weight Change` = mean(`Weight Change (lbs)`, na.rm = TRUE),
model_stress_age <- lm(`Weight Change (lbs)` ~ `High Stress Risk` * age_group, data = Health)

lm(formula = `Weight Change (lbs)` ~ `High Stress Risk` * age_group, 
    data = Health)
